		<p>Blessings Chola is from Kashishi village in Central Province. Her parents are both farmers. Her favorite subject is math and she would like to be an accountant. Her nominator wrote that "Blessings is always the first student to volunteer to help me with any co-curricular activities, participates in every discussion, is not afraid to challenge herself academically and confidently speaks out when she does not understand a concept". She is the top student in her class. Nobody in her family has ever gone beyond Grade 9.<a href = "../pages/more"><span style="color:blue"> More...</span></a></p>
